"Time to get real" is right.

@gfriedma, an economist who has spent decades studying our health care system, says via @USATODAY, "Is Medicare for All bold? Absolutely. Is it reasonable? You bet." 

Add economists to the list of #MedicareForAll supporters.https://www.usatoday.com/story/opinion/2019/04/08/medicare-for-all-reasonable-practical-health-care-reform-column/3393034002/ …

Two years ago, Medicare for All was considered unrealistic and Bernie’s bill in the Senate had zero co-sponsors.

@PramilaJayapal’s new bill that was just introduced has over 100 co-sponsors.

It’s also supported by 70% of Americans. This is how progress happens.

2019 is the year of #MedicareForAll!

@RepJayapal is introducing the Medicare for All Act of 2019  & she has sent a letter to congressional colleagues asking them to sign on to the bill.

